Grupo Bimbo, Sara Lee Bakery Deal Gets U.S. Approval

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-10-21T19:03:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/grupo-bimbo-sara-lee-bakery-deal-gets-u-s-approval-correct-.html
Grupo Bimbo SAB won U.S. regulatory
approval to buy  Sara Lee Corp. (SLE) ’s North American Fresh Bakery
business, reducing the acquisition price to $709 million from
$959 million.  Grupo Bimbo agreed to sell some sliced bread brands and
related assets to meet U.S. Justice Department requirements,
Sara Lee said in a statement.  Monica Breton, a spokeswoman for Bimbo, didn’t immediately
return a voice message seeking comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivek Shankar in  San Francisco  at 
